title: Super Bowl LV Top Props & Bets: Focus on Tyreek Hill & Mike Evans receiving yards (Football 2/3)
description:
Jacob Gibbs joins Will Brinson to break down his top 3 props for Super Bowl LV. Jacob dishes out useful nuggets and sides to target with Tyreek Hill and Mike Evans receiving yards props. 
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
